emory_usage_rate' 异常上升。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod 'redis-cart-0' 的 'pod_cpu_usage' 变化比为 0.7601。Node 'aiops-k8s-05' 的 'node_memory_usage_rate' 变化比为 0.3918。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "redis-cart-0 is the root cause due to high pod_cpu_usage leading to node_memory_usage_rate exhaustion."}
